Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:14.24,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know what I should do now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.41,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}With every strength I can take to break enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:34.10,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絶縁體のような表情で　抵抗を嫌う口実を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:38.35,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}共振拒む理由なんて　単純すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.41,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:55.95,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I won't let you down come along with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.71,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Taking back my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:03.42,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.67,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}確信はその手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:11.97,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm waiting for till the break of dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:14.47,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Taking back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}錆付いた意志でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.10,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:23.77,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}革命に似た Calling back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.98,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tell me what's wrong with the society
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.98,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}that everybody is saying OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Low resistance of high zest inner cells
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:33.82,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Rebuild the coil there is no lie
